<h1>Echo Canceller</h1>

<p>The Echo CancellerÂ¨ menu option in Elastix allows you to enable and disable echo cancellation via software. It also shows the current state of this feature (Active or Inactive).</p>

<div><img src="/images/help/pbx/echo_canceller.jpg" border="0"></div>
